---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { links } from '../data/links';
import { assets } from '../data/assets';
---
<MainLayout title="Music | Corrine J Blackthorn">
  <section>
    <div class="container split">
      <div>
        <span class="kicker">Glass & Thorns</span>
        <h1>Music</h1>
        <p>Some experiences are difficult to explain through technology or writing. Music gives those experiences another voice.</p>
        <p>Glass & Thorns is my artist project exploring identity, transformation, resilience, growth, and becoming who we are meant to be.</p>
        <p>My Body Isn't Home Anymore is the first public step in that journey, with more music and creative projects planned for the future.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button" href={links.music.spotify}>Spotify</a>
          <a class="button" href={links.music.appleMusic}>Apple Music</a>
          <a class="button" href={links.music.youtube}>YouTube</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="image-frame"><img src={assets.brandImages.glassAndThorns} alt="Glass & Thorns branding" loading="lazy" /></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quote-band"><div class="container"><blockquote>Art gives language to the parts of us that survived before we had words.</blockquote></div></section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card"><h3>Glass & Thorns</h3><p>The primary music project and home for current releases.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>Current Release</h3><p>My Body Isn't Home Anymore is the first public release from Glass & Thorns.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>Why Music</h3><p>Music creates space for emotions, stories, and experiences that do not always fit neatly into other forms of communication.</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>